com.paydiant.android.ui.service.giftaccount

Class GiftAccountManagementListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paydiant.android.ui.service.giftaccount.GiftAccountManagementListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IGiftAccountManagementListener

    public class GiftAccountManagementListenerAdapter
extends Object
implements IGiftAccountManagementListener
    Provides empty implementation for IGiftAccountManagementListener interface. Any classes that need to use a subset of the IGiftAccountManagementListener methods can utilize this adapter class by overriding the required methods. 

           GiftAccountManagementListenerAdapter giftAccountManagementListenerAdapter = new GiftAccountManagementListenerAdapter() {
          @Override
          public void onRetrieveLoadConfigurationSuccess(LoadConfiguration loadConfiguration) {
          }
      };
      iGiftAccountManagementService.setGiftAccountManagementListener(giftAccountManagementListenerAdapter);
    Note: App developers are encouraged to use the ListenerAdapter implementations whenever possible as the Listener interfaces might get updated with new functionality/methods from one SDK release to the other. Therefore using a ListenerAdapter will make sure that there wont be any compilation issues due to unimplemented methods during a SDK upgrade.

    Since:
    4.1.0.1
    Author:
    Paydiant
